            <description><![CDATA[我很高兴地宣布 JsonSage 的首次发布！JsonSage 是一个智能的 JSON 处理工作流系统，旨在简化 JSON 数据的验证、转换和监控过程。]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>我很高兴地宣布 JsonSage 的首次发布！JsonSage 是一个智能的 JSON 处理工作流系统，旨在简化 JSON 数据的验证、转换和监控过程。</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="为什么创建-jsonsage">为什么创建 JsonSage？<a href="https://hongping1963-source.github.io/jsonsage/blog/introducing-jsonsage#%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA-jsonsage" class="hash-link" aria-label="为什么创建 JsonSage？的直接链接" title="为什么创建 JsonSage？的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<p>在现代软件开发中，JSON 已经成为最广泛使用的数据交换格式。然而，随着项目规模的增长，JSON 数据的处理变得越来越复杂：</p>
<ul>
<li>需要实时监控多个 JSON 文件的变化</li>
<li>需要验证复杂的数据结构</li>
<li>需要进行各种数据转换</li>
<li>需要确保高性能和可靠性</li>
</ul>
<p>JsonSage 就是为了解决这些挑战而创建的。</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="主要特性">主要特性<a href="https://hongping1963-source.github.io/jsonsage/blog/introducing-jsonsage#%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7" class="hash-link" aria-label="主要特性的直接链接" title="主要特性的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="1-智能监控">1. 智能监控<a href="https://hongping1963-source.github.io/jsonsage/blog/introducing-jsonsage#1-%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7" class="hash-link" aria-label="1. 智能监控的直接链接" title="1. 智能监控的直接链接">​</a></h3>
<p>JsonSage 提供了强大的文件监控功能：</p>
<div class="language-typescript codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_biex"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-typescript codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">const</span><span class="token plain"> sage </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token keyword" style="color:#00009f">new</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token class-name">JsonSage</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">{</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  watchPath</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'./data'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  patterns</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">[</span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'**/*.json'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">]</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  exclude</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">[</span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'**/node_modules/**'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">]</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">}</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">;</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">sage</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">.</span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">on</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token string" style="color:#e3116c">'fileChange'</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token plain">event</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">)</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">=&gt;</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">{</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain">  </span><span class="token builtin">console</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">.</span><span class="token function" style="color:#d73a49">log</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">(</span><span class="token template-string template-punctuation string" style="color:#e3116c">`</span><span class="token template-string string" style="color:#e3116c">文件 </span><span class="token template-string interpolation interpolation-punctuation punctuation" style="color:#393A34">${