<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="2-强大的验证">2. 强大的验证<a href="https://hongping1963-source.github.io/jsonsage/blog/introducing-jsonsage#2-%E5%BC%BA%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81" class="hash-link" aria-label="2. 强大的验证的直接链接" title="2. 强大的验证的直接链接">​</a></h3>
